response.overview: From the 1960s to the 1980s, evangelist Jim Baker and his ambitious wife, Tammy Faye, rose from humble beginnings to build an empire based on big-time evangelical Christianity--only for the couple to fall from grace because of some all-too-human sins.
response.tagline: Sometimes in life, you have to take your lashes.
response.title: The Eyes of Tammy Faye
